// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1084 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: a49aebc8-af46-56f5-8b89-3ec021e58e01

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:5* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:6* OR ImageFileName = *redhat/ubi9:*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
